Hornby Track Master is a software tool to design Hornby Railways train tracks.
Gameplay
Hornby Track-Master is a birds eye 2D Planning tool. It is unlike Hornby Virtual Railway. HVR1 Uses a 3D Planning Enviroment in witch you plan, build and test you layout. How ever, being HVR Being released many years ago has bad Graphics. Also Hornby Track-Master developes a Shopping list for every thing needed to build it, but it has no 3D where as HVR Dose but dose Develope a shopping list.
Users select pieces of track from lists and places them where the user wishs. Track-Master use birds eye view to work. Track, Platforms, turntables etc can be added, once completed the software developes a printable shopping list2 which see people can go out and but the things they need with out buying to much and wasting it or buying to less and having to go back
Hornby Track-Master (2011)
Hornby is soon3 about to Release a new program. This program is called Track-Master, Track-Master is a 2D planning Enviroment. People select pieces of track from lists and places them where the user wishs. Track-Master use birds eye view to work. Track, Platforms, turntables etc can be added, once completed the software developes a printable shopping list which see people can go out and but the things they need with out buying to much and wasting it or buying to less and having to go back
